  "analyst_note": "CVE-2021-44832: RCE in Apache Log4j 2.x < 2.17.1 when the attacker has write access to the logging configuration. Lower severity than CVE-2021-44228 (Log4Shell) but still critical in shared/cloud environments. Log4j is an embedded library — direct remote version detection is not possible. Treat as inconclusive and confirm via authenticated code review or SBOM analysis. Upgrade to Log4j 2.17.1 (Java 8), 2.12.4 (Java 7), or 2.3.2 (Java 6).",
